Here a few instructions for my game :)

1.) This game is hard. You have to be careful.
2.) It's a console game. You have to enter words to play this game.
3.) This game is in english.
4.) You will have to buy equipment. If you fight without, you loose.
5.) There is scoreboard integrated. If you close the app the scoreboared will be deleted.
6.) Have fun and try to end this game :P
